1/1 1/2 1/3 1/4 1/5 ...
2/1 2/2 2/3 2/4
3/1 3/2 3/3
4/1 4/2
5/1

numerator  : 1 1 2 3 2 1 1 2 3 4 5 4 3 2 1 .....
denominator: 1 2 1 1 2 3 4 3 2 1 1 2 3 4 5 6 5 ....
 [1] [5] [9] [13] ...
 [3] [7] [11] ....
 
numerator : 
end(i)    = sum(1 -> i)[4n-3]
          = 2(i^2+i) -3i
          = 2i^2-i

2x^2 -x - v = 0
x = (1 + sqrt(1+8*v))/4

denominator:
end(i) = sum(1->i)[4n-1]
       = 2(i^2+i) - i
       = 2i^2+i
       
2x^2 +x - v
x = (-1 + sqrt(1+8*v))/4
